            , was indicted for a Misdemeanor, in <rs id="t17230227-68-off372" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17230227-68-off372" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17230227-68-off372" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               solliciting and perswading 
                     <persName id="t17230227-68-person357">
                        Edward 
                        Cheesebrook 
                     <interp inst="t17230227-68-person357" type="surname" value="Cheesebrook"></interp>
